cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a distributed relay selection scheme for UAV communication networks.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper uses a many-to-many matching game approach to optimize the relay selection process.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper considers a multi-radio and multi-channel communication system.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with optimizing the performance of a distributed system without a central controller.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as UAV communication networks may involve multimedia data transmission.
